1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,970
You and I have been in many situations when someone burst in and said, I've got good news.

2
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:11,411
Immediately, this person gets 100% attention from everyone present.

3
00:00:11,759 --> 00:00:14,289
Good news does more than get attention.

4
00:00:14,401 --> 00:00:16,289
Good news pleases people.

5
00:00:16,401 --> 00:00:18,769
Good news develops enthusiasm.

6
00:00:18,961 --> 00:00:21,810
Good news even promotes good digestion.

7
00:00:22,641 --> 00:00:29,970
Just because there are more broadcasters of bad news than there are broadcasters of good news, don't be misled.

8
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:37,970
No one ever won a friend, no one ever made money, no one ever accomplished anything by broadcasting bad news.

9
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:41,171
Transmit good news to your family.

10
00:00:41,361 --> 00:00:43,730
Tell them the good that happened today.

11
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:50,211
Recall the amusing, pleasant things you experienced and let the unpleasant things stay buried.

12
00:00:51,361 --> 00:00:53,009
Spread good news.

13
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:55,250
It's pointless to pass on the bad.

14
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:58,371
It only makes your family worry, makes them nervous.

15
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:01,330
Bring home some sunlight every day.

16
00:01:02,161 --> 00:01:05,970
Ever notice how seldom children complain about the weather?

17
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:14,289
They take hot weather in stride until the negative news core educate them to be conscious of unpleasant temperatures.

18
00:01:14,641 --> 00:01:21,009
Make it a habit always to speak favorably about the weather, regardless of what the weather actually is.

19
00:01:21,201 --> 00:01:26,371
Complaining about the weather makes you more miserable, and it spreads misery to others.

20
00:01:26,961 --> 00:01:29,891
Broadcast good news about how you feel.

21
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:32,451
Be an I-feel-great person.

22
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:37,970
Just say, I feel great, at every possible opportunity, and you will feel better.

23
00:01:38,161 --> 00:01:44,289
By the same token, tell people, I feel awful, just awful, and you will feel worse.

24
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:49,810
How we feel is in large part determined by how we think we feel.

25
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:55,411
Remember, too, that other people want to be around alive, enthusiastic people.

26
00:01:55,681 --> 00:01:59,810
Being around complainers and half-dead people is uncomfortable.

27
00:02:00,641 --> 00:02:03,730
Transmit good news to the people you work with.

28
00:02:03,921 --> 00:02:05,330
Give them encouragement.

29
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,651
Compliment them at every opportunity.

30
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:11,330
Tell them about the positive things the company is doing.

31
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,931
Listen to their problems.

32
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:13,970
Be helpful.

33
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:16,851
Encourage people and win their support.

